Checkpoint 1:

    Create a new project with an app.js, package.json, process.env, routes/routes.js, views/index.ejs, public/styles.css, and controllers/gameController.js files
    Use the DataMuse API 

Links to an external site. to load 10 random words. 
Use the controller and view files to display your words on the website.
Write a function in the controller to create a 15x15 2D grid containing your words and filled with random letters. Console.log the grid.
Update the view so that the grid is displayed on the website.
Update the controller so that the 10 words are thematic (an option from DataMuse).